# Commands Used - This document contains the commands used to configure and deploy the CI/CD pipeline.

## System Information -
hostname
hostnamectl
ip addr
java -version

## Git Commands - 
git clone <repository-url>
git status
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git push origin main

## Maven Commands
mvn clean
mvn compile
mvn test
mvn package
mvn deploy

## Jenkins Commands
systemctl start jenkins
systemctl stop jenkins
systemctl restart jenkins
systemctl status jenkins

## Nexus Commands
systemctl start nexus
systemctl stop nexus
systemctl restart nexus
systemctl status nexus

## Tomcat Commands
./startup.sh
./shutdown.sh

## Linux Commands
pwd
ls -l
cd
mkdir
chmod
chown
